story.text: Throat feels a tingle - hopefully not a sickness. Things are well at work and my trip to NYC is shaping up well.
Excited to hang out with Ben, Brittany and the Kids soon!
I had a tough time this weekend missing my family. I hate that they are so set on wasting away in Texas - but so be it.
